edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.presentationlayer.view
Class MapPhaseListener

java.lang.Object
  edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.presentationlayer.view.MapPhaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, EventListener, PhaseListener
public class MapPhaseListener
extends Object
implements PhaseListener

Implements a JSF Phase Listener to manage the changedProperties property of MapModel. The changedProperties have to be reset for each request because they still might be set from the request before. Even more, if the web page is requested for the first time, all properties need to be marked as changed for being converted correctly.

Author:
Stefan
